-- Assurant Says Superstorm Cost Insurer as Much as $220 Million
-- B y   Z a c h a r y   T r a c e r
-- 2012-12-18T21:19:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-18/assurant-says-superstorm-cost-insurer-as-much-as-220-million.html
Assurant Inc. (AIZ) , the insurer of
foreclosed homes, said superstorm Sandy cost the specialty
property unit $200 million to $220 million.  The figures are before tax and after reinsurance, the New
York-based company said today in a statement distributed by PR
Newswire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zachary Tracer in New York at 
 ztracer1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
